author: kentam
msg: A simple form of external control implementation binding.  The infrastructure now supports a properties file "controlbindings.properties" -- property keys are control bean classnames, mapped to values that are control implementation classnames.
Added a DRT test to illustrate usage.  I'll update the wiki w/ more details.
This is meant largely as a proof-of-concept; a generalized approach to external configuration (potentially incorporating integration with other lightweight frameworks) will eventually obsolete this.
